name: Rafael Fernandez

jv_history.source_quote: appointed Rafael Fernández Bautista as a new partner ... Rafael Fernández joins Broset

what_you_do: Rafael is a certified Life Coach who has helped over 170 clients create meaningful, lasting change since 2020.
who_you_serve: Rafael helps people develop deeper self-understanding, work through emotional challenges, and gain the clarity and confidence to move forward in their lives, relationships, and careers.
social_proof: Rafael received his primary coaching training under Dr. Alok Kanojia (MD, MPH), and also trained with former Amazon VP Ethan Evans. He has over 4,000 hours of coaching experience.
business_focus: Rafael helps clients achieve external goals while building the self-awareness and emotional strength needed for lasting growth.
service_provided: life coaching, career coaching, performance coaching
